  "keyFeatures": [
    "Map gamepad buttons and analog sticks to keyboard keys and mouse controls",
    "Support for macros combining keystrokes, mouse events, and scripts",
    "Multiple switchable mapping sets (up to 8) per gamepad",
    "Auto-profiles: automatically load profiles based on the active application window",
    "SDL2 game controller mapping support for non-standard gamepads",
    "D-Bus interface for programmatic control on Linux",
    "Supports X.org, Wayland, and Windows",
    "Gyroscope and accelerometer sensor input support",
    "Gamepad calibration tool",
    "Available as Flatpak, AppImage, DEB, RPM, and Windows installer"
  ],
